To do user emuneration on Kali:
Step 01: Type 'theHarvester' on your kali terminal => Enter
Step 02: Type 'theHarvester --help' to know about your harvester tool => Enter
Step 03: Type 'theHarvester -d (domanin name, exp: gmail.com) -l 250 -b google => Enter

To install modules:
Step 01: Type 'marketplace refresh' => Enter
Step 02: Type 'marketplace install all' => Enter

Passively get intel in Kali Linux: 
Step 01: After installing modules, Type 'modules load hackertarget' => Enter
Step 02: Type 'options'
Step 03: Type 'options set source (domain name, exp: gmail.com) 
Step 04: Type 'info'
Step 05: Type 'run'
Step 06: Type 'show hosts'
